OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781172387
OL,3,CGovernment confirms hidden camera
OL,4,Cdiscovered in offices
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Home Office Minister
OL,7,FLord Hanson confirmed to the House of
OL,8,FLords that a camera was discovered
OL,9,Fduring routine checks.
OL,11,FHanson said that the device was found
OL,12,Fin a communal area of the MHCLG
OL,13,Fbuilding and was not near any
OL,14,Fministerial offices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781172387
OL,3,CGovernment confirms hidden camera
OL,4,Cdiscovered in offices
OL,6,FThe complex, located near the Houses
OL,7,Fof Parliament, is the base for the
OL,8,FHome Office, responsible for policing
OL,9,Fand national security and MHCLG, which
OL,10,Ftook decisions relating to the
OL,11,Fplanning permission for the
OL,12,Fcontroversial new Chinese embassy in
OL,13,FLondon.
OL,15,FWhen questioned about this, Hanson
OL,16,Fassured members that this discovery
OL,17,Fdid not point to foreign interference.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
