OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781172387
OL,3,CGovernment confirms hidden camera
OL,4,Cdiscovered in offices
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe report states that there is no
OL,12,Fsuggestion that Russian or Chinese
OL,13,Fagents are responsible for the device.
OL,15,FAn MHCLG spokesperson said: "We do not
OL,16,Fcomment on security matters."
OL,18,FShadow minister, Alex Burghart told
OL,19,FThe i Paper: "This is a serious
OL,20,Fincident that demands urgent
OL,21,Finvestigation".
