CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781172387
OL,3,CGovernment confirms hidden camera
OL,4,Cdiscovered in offices
OL,6,F"The discovery of a hidden camera
OL,7,Finside a building that occupies the
OL,8,FHome Office and other departments
OL,9,Fraises questions about the security of
OL,10,Fgovernment departments and those
OL,11,Fseeking to undermine them."
OL,13,FHe added: "We urgently need to know
OL,14,Fwho was responsible, how long this
OL,15,Fdevice was in place and whether any
OL,16,Fsensitive or classified information
OL,17,Fhas been compromised."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]uD@KOUyD@VO]
